            <i class="fa fa-download" aria-hidden="true"></i> <a href="https://res.cloudinary.com/dn4nxz7f0/raw/upload/v1580485796/HTML%20table%20to%20excel/jquery.table2excel.min_bdjf5z.rar" download>Download File Table2Excel</a></p>
  
            <p>Sau đó các bạn sẽ giải nén file và tạo ra cấu trúc thư mục cây như sau: </p>
            <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dn4nxz7f0/image/upload/v1580486733/HTML%20table%20to%20excel/table2excel_twjj79.svg"  width="200" height="200" alt="Table2Excel">
            <p>Các bạn nhập đoạn code này vào <b>trangchinh.html</b>: </p>
            <pre><code class="html">&#60;!doctype html&#62; <br /> &#60;html lang="en"&#62; <br /> &#60;head&#62; <br /> &#60;title&#62;Trang Chính&#60;/title&#62; <br />&#60;meta charset="utf-8"&#62; <br /> &#60;meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no"&#62; <br />&#60;link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous"&#62; <br /> &#60;/head&#62; <br /> &#60;body&#62; <br />&#60;script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-q8i/X+965DzO0rT7abK41JStQIAqVgRVzpbzo5smXKp4YfRvH+8abtTE1Pi6jizo" crossorigin="anonymous"&#62;&#60;/script&#62; <br /> &#60;script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-UO2eT0CpHqdSJQ6hJty5KVphtPhzWj9WO1clHTMGa3JDZwrnQq4sF86dIHNDz0W1" crossorigin="anonymous"&#62;&#60;/script&#62; <br /> &#60;script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JjSmVgyd0p3pXB1rRibZUAYoIIy6OrQ6VrjIEaFf/nJGzIxFDsf4x0xIM+B07jRM" crossorigin="anonymous"&#62;&#60;/script&#62; <br /> &#60;script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.1/jquery.min.js"&#62;&#60;/script&#62; <br /> &#60;script src="./jquery.table2excel.min.js"&#62;&#60;/script&#62;<br />&#60;/body&#62; <br />&#60;/html&#62;<br /></code></pre>
          <p>Sau khi đã thêm được file jquery.table2excel.min.js vào trang HTML thì bạn nhập một bảng như ví dụ sau đây: </p>
          <table class="table" id="table2excel">
